_sText:
In Uvalno village, where I live, is villa next to my house. Fortunately it is my friend's villa, so he agreed with reconstruction his house to CSS map (His name is Ulicny  so I named map after him "Ulicni"). He provided  groundplans and allowed me to take some panorama photos. I worked on this almost 3 months.

This is my second reconstruction project of Uvalno village, so it is not playable because of low fps (there are only 3 player start of each side).

I wanted participate on Realistic Mapping Contest with villa, but I decided to post uvalno_kostel to the contest.

I remade this map to playable hostage rescue version,

If you like this one, check all of my maps here
This map or its parts is also used in my singleplayer mod

Have a fun
Dinus Saurus
